<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Terms & Conditions - B A Furniture</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background-color: white;
      color: #333;
    }

    .salesmobie {
      display: none;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 768px) {
      .salesmobie {
        text-align: center;
        background-color: goldenrod;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 5px;
        display: block;
      }
    }

    .term {
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      border: 2px solid goldenrod;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(218, 165, 32, 0.2);
    }

    .termhead {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .termhead h1 {
      color: goldenrod;
      font-size: 32px;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .termbody {
      color: #555;
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      padding: 0 10px;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    ul li {
      list-style-type: disc;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .termheadbody {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .container1 {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 50%;
      box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .container1 img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .container1 img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.1);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <%- include('component/navbar') %>
  <%- include('component/mobilenav') %>

  <div class="salesmobie">
    Get 15% off your next furniture order!
  </div>

  <section class="term">
    <div class="termhead">
      <h1>Terms & Conditions</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="termbody">
      <ul>
        <li>You may cancel your furniture order any time before it is processed. Once shipped, our return & exchange policy applies.</li>
        <li>Furniture items are carefully inspected before shipping. Minor variations in color or texture are part of the natural characteristics of wood and upholstery and are not considered defects.</li>
        <li>If a product is damaged in transit, please contact us within 48 hours for resolution.</li>
        <li>Discounted items and promotional offers are non-refundable but may be exchangeable subject to stock availability.</li>
        <li>All custom-made furniture orders are final and non-refundable after confirmation.</li>
        <li>If you are applying a discount or promo code, ensure it is valid at the time of checkout. Orders with expired or invalid codes may be canceled.</li>
        <li>Returns are only accepted for unused, undamaged furniture in original packaging within 7 days.</li>
        <li>Delivery timelines may vary by location, especially for made-to-order furniture. Any delay due to unforeseen events will be communicated.</li>
        <li>Shipping and handling charges are non-refundable. Additional charges may apply for re-delivery attempts.</li>
        <li>For customer service, contact us at <a href="mailto:care@bafurniture.pk" style="color: goldenrod;">care@bafurniture.pk</a> or call us at <a href="tel:+923006020082" style="color: goldenrod;">+92 300 6020082</a>.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="termhead">
      <h1>Social Accounts</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="termheadbody">
      <div class="container1">
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/PentaSports.pk" target="_blank">
          <img src="/images/facebook.png" alt="Facebook" />
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="container1">
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/penta.pk/" target="_blank">
          <img src="/images/instgaram.jpg" alt="Instagram" />
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="container1">
        <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send/?phone=923338420501&text&type=phone_number&app_absent=0" target="_blank">
          <img src="/images/whastapp.png" alt="WhatsApp" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('component/footer') %>

</body>
</html>
